if {Thief.CollectTreasure} == false:
	Narrator: The Thief marvels at her fathe- the king's hoard. With so much wealth, surely no one would miss a bit of treasure.
	Narrator: ... and the townsfolk would certainly appreciate it!
	Narrator: The Thief loads up on loot and continues her tale.
	set {Thief.CollectTreasure} = true
	[signal arg="collect_treasure"]
else:
	Narrator: There's still plenty of gold left. The Thief doesn't think she'll need to take any more.
